<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Registro - BookBarber Online</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; background: #0f0f0f; color: #fff; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; height: 100vh; margin: 0; }
        .reg-card { background: #1a1a1a; padding: 40px; border-radius: 15px; border: 1px solid #333; width: 100%; max-width: 400px; text-align: center; }
        input { width: 100%; padding: 12px; margin: 10px 0; background: #2a2a2a; border: 1px solid #444; color: white; border-radius: 8px; box-sizing: border-box; }
        button { width: 100%; padding: 12px; background: #f39c12; border: none; color: black; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; margin-top: 10px; }
        .logo { font-size: 24px; color: #f39c12; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="reg-card">
        <div class="logo">BookBarber Online</div>
        <p>Crea tu cuenta y empieza tus 30 días gratis</p>
        <form action="/auth/registro" method="POST">
            <input type="text" name="nombre_barberia" placeholder="Nombre de tu Barbería" required>
            <input type="text" name="whatsapp" placeholder="Tu WhatsApp (ej: 351...)" required>
            <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Crea una contraseña" required>
            <button type="submit">EMPEZAR PRUEBA GRATUITA</button>
        </form>
        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 20px;">&copy; MedinSur Dev</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
